00:04:47,220 --> 00:04:48,660
If anything, the opposite.

74
00:04:48,660 --> 00:04:50,060
How so, Ma'am?

75
00:04:50,060 --> 00:04:52,620
I was due to rotate
Hari from Danny's squad,

76
00:04:52,620 --> 00:04:55,260
