more jobs with him. Really?

78
00:04:58,180 --> 00:05:00,100
When did he say this?

79
00:05:00,100 --> 00:05:02,380
Couple of days
before the Abbots Lane op.

80
00:05:02,380 --> 00:05:05,740
You mean a couple of days before
the op that got Danny killed?

81
00:05:05,740 --> 00:05:07,660
I was all set to disband
Danny's team

82
00:05:07,660 --> 00:05:09,500
after the shooting
of Ronan Murphy

83
00:05:09,500 --> 00:05:12,500
and there is no way you're going
to pin some blame on me

84
