just because you're struggling
to find a scapegoat.

85
00:05:14,780 --> 00:05:17,180
Thank you, Ma'am.
You've been very helpful.

86
00:06:02,980 --> 00:06:06,820
'AC-12.' DC Fleming. Put me through
