the mobile network provider to see

97
00:06:41,940 --> 00:06:45,020
what information
we can get about the number. Great.

98
00:06:45,020 --> 00:06:47,500
Tell Kate I want her on
Hari Bains round the clock.

99
00:06:47,500 --> 00:06:48,860
Yeah, will do, Gaffer.

100
00:07:11,060 --> 00:07:13,700
'What the
bloody hell are you playing at?

101
00:07:13,700 --> 00:07:15,220
'Making a call from a public box?

102
00:07:15,220 --> 00:07:17,500
'That's why we sent you
the unregistered mobiles.'

103
00:07:17,500 --> 00:07:19,740
The text came through to my own
phone, so I thought...

104
00:07:19,740 --> 00:07:21,980
'Yeah, well, we had to get
a message to you urgently

105
00:07:21,980 --> 00:07:25,020
'and you weren't answering.
You're being watched by AC-12.'

106
00:07:25,020 --> 00:07:27,540
I didn't see anyone.
'What did the text say?'

107
00:07:27,540 --> 00:07:28,900
"Sit tight. Act normal."

108
00:07:28,900 --> 00:07:31,740
So how's this acting normal?
Dickhead.

109
00:07:41,620 --> 00:07:43,260
All right? All right?

110
00:07:43,260 --> 00:07:46,580
Look, for my two penn'orth, I
think we're flogging a dead horse

111
00:07:46,580 --> 00:07:48,100
with Bains and Brickford.

112
00:07:48,100 --> 00:07:50,140
Rod Kennedy killed Danny Waldron,

113
00:07:50,140 --> 00:07:52,380
couldn't handle the guilt,
he topped himself.

114
00:07:52,380 --> 00:07:53,820
Maybe it wasn't suicide.

115
00:07:53,820 --> 00:07:56,740
We ought to request a second
postmortem on Rod Kennedy's body.

116
00:07:56,740 --> 00:07:58,900
The first one was only
looking for cause of death.

117
00:07:58,900 --> 00:08:00,620
