pathologist

118
00:08:00,620 --> 00:08:02,420
looking for evidence of crime.

119
00:08:03,580 --> 00:08:04,620
Sure.

120
00:08:04,620 --> 00:08:06,780
Leave that with me. Cheers.

121
00:08:06,780 --> 00:08:08,380
Do you like chilli?

122
00:08:08,380 --> 00:08:10,300
The food.

123
00:08:10,300 --> 00:08:12,220
Not the country.

124
00:08:12,220 --> 00:08:14,860
I've got a pot... on the simmer.

125
00:08:17,300 --> 00:08:18,900
