126
00:08:20,380 --> 00:08:22,100
No, I haven't, actually.

127
00:08:22,100 --> 00:08:24,100
Well?

128
00:08:24,100 --> 00:08:25,740
Yeah.

129
00:08:28,620 --> 00:08:30,780
