185
00:11:57,620 --> 00:11:59,500
Do you recognise the image? Yeah.

186
00:12:01,180 --> 00:12:03,740
Do you recall
the name of this location? Yes.

187
00:12:05,620 --> 00:12:07,900
Mr Nash, you're not in any trouble.

188
00:12:07,900 --> 00:12:09,780
