00:14:48,020 --> 00:14:49,460
Or a few of you would.

236
00:14:51,460 --> 00:14:52,580
With a few of them.

237
00:14:54,220 --> 00:14:58,940
The abuse always took place within Sands
View? No, not always. There was, erm...

238
00:14:58,940 --> 00:15:01,300
sometimes there'd
be a car or a minibus

239
00:15:01,300 --> 00:15:04,820
and they'd take us to a hotel,
or a guesthouse, or some big...

